@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam BorderColor #333333
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
title Architecture Review and Approval Sequence
participant Architect
participant "Architecture Repository" as AR
participant "Conformance Engine" as CE
participant "Domain Council" as DC
participant "Architecture Board" as AB
participant "Assurance Service" as AS
Architect -> AR : submit architecture change
AR -> CE : validate standards and traceability
CE --> AR : conformance report
AR -> DC : request domain review
DC --> AR : recommendation
AR -> AB : decision package
AB -> AS : request assurance evidence
AS --> AB : confidence assessment
AB --> Architect : approve / condition / reject
AB -> AR : publish decision and rationale
@enduml
